00:17:36.889 --> 00:17:39.642
-Desligue e volte a ligar.
-[suspira dramaticamente]

00:17:39.725 --> 00:17:41.644
—[grita]
—[Jin-woo] Ainda não funciona?

00:17:41.727 --> 00:17:44.272
— Nem pensar.
